messages.message: <!here>, Does anyone know the impact if I remove `cur_status` field from documentation? We have run into an issue where some of the sub-fields under `cur_status` field are erratic. In some status API calls, they are returned correctly and in others they are not. Documentation Link: `https://www.instabase.com/docs/content/apis/flow-apis.html`
C1 trusted our Status API and got burnt by it.
